  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Hameau de Kashmir is on a bed and breakfast basis. </p>
<p>A buffet breakfast with a range of local breads, pastries, meats, cheeses, jams, honey, fruit juice and additional hot options is served between 7.30-9.30am each day. </p>
<p>You have the option to upgrade to half board, which includes a three course dinner with a choice of main.  Christmas Eve and New Year's Eve Gala Dinners are including if taking half board over this period</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Kashmir provides the ultimate ski convenience alongside a beautifully decorated interior with a Himalayan theme and excellent service. You can enjoy stunning views from the property and the lively atmosphere of <a data-udi="umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8}" title="Val Thorens">Val Thorens</a> as this peaceful accommodation is located just a five minute walk from the resort centre and shops.</p>
<h2>Wellness and relaxation</h2>
<p>After an active day of skiing or snowboarding, you can relax in the hotel's sauna, hot tub, or indoor pool which offers incredible views of the surrounding mountains. There is also a relaxation area available for anyone looking for some quiet time. Massages and other beauty treatments can be booked through the hotel if you truly want to splurge on something nice for yourself. A compact fitness room equipped with a range of exercise machines is available if you want to stay in shape.</p>
<h2>Superior suites</h2>
<p>The authentic and refined atmosphere the suites provide makes this property an idyllic place to stay on your ski holiday. Not only are the hotel suites cosy and finished to a high standard, you will also get to enjoy a hearty skiers breakfast and access to the spa, pool and gym.</p>
<h2>Easy slope access</h2>
<p>The Residence Hameau de Kashmir is located close to the entrance of Val Thorens and with a prime spot at the base of the Plein Sud piste. These apartments offer ski-in, ski-out access, making it simple to reach the renowned Three Valleys. In addition, many of the apartments have magnificent views of the whole resort and the mountains surrounding it. If you are looking for a place to grab a bite to eat or a drink, the vibrant resort centre is close by, where there is a wide selection of restaurants and bars to cater to everyone's tastes. If you prefer, you can also upgrade to have breakfast and/or dinner at the restaurant that is located on the property.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
