  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>are around 40m² sleeping two to three people. Junior Suites have a double bed in a spacious alcove with sliding door and an additional single bedroom.</p>
<p><strong>Family Suites </strong>are around 45m² sleeping two to four people, with one double bedroom and one twin bedroom</p>
<p><strong>Prestige Suites </strong>are around 80m² sleeping two to five people. Prestige Suites have a d<span>ouble bedroom and twin bedroom, and an additional single bed either in the living room or on a mezzanine overlooking the living area. </span></p>
<p><span>Daily housekeeping is included.</span></p>
<p><strong>Room facilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Balcony with mountain views</li>
<li>Bathrobes </li>
<li>Slippers</li>
<li>Cable/satellite TV</li>
<li>Hair dryer</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment or shower room</li>
<li>Towels (changed daily)</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Baby cots are available on request, free of charge. Sheets and mattress are not provided. </li>
<li>Baby bath and bottle warmer are available (pre-bookable)</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
